STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jeffery L. MANESS. No. 517P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 5, 2006. Jeffery L. Maness, Pro Se. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Garland N. Yates, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 25th day of September 2006 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Moore County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in Conference this the 5th day of October 2006."
